      "rationale": "Testing was performed under a single load configuration (ASTM F1717 static compression-bending at 5 mm/min crosshead speed) at ambient temperature. No variation in loading rate, angle, or environmental conditions was explored. This limits the breadth of validation evidence and results in an achieved level of 1, below the required level of 2. This gap is acknowledged and accepted given the regulatory precedent for F1717 as a standardized surrogate test."
